<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <title>3-Column Preview Card Component</title>
    <meta name="description" content="3-Column Preview Card Component" />
    <meta name="author" content="Ashley Colman" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="scss/main.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Big+Shoulders+Display:wght@700&family=Lexend+Deca&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <section id="grid">
            <div class="card--orange card1">
                <div class="card__wrapper">
                    <img class="card__icon" src="images/icon-sedans.svg" alt="Sedan." />
                    <h1 class="card__h1">SEDANS</h1>
                    <p class="card__p">Choose a sedan for its affordability and excellent fuel economy. Ideal for cruising in the city or on your next road trip.</p>
                    <button class="card__button card__button--orange">Learn More</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card--cyan card2">
                <div class="card__wrapper">
                    <img class="card__icon" src="images/icon-suvs.svg" alt="SUV." />
                    <h1 class="card__h1">SUVS</h1>
                    <p class="card__p">Take an SUV for its spacious interior, power, and versatility. Perfect for your next family vacation and off-raod adventures.</p>
                    <button class="card__button card__button--cyan">Learn More</button>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="card--dark-cyan card3">
                <div class="card__wrapper">
                    <img class="card__icon" src="images/icon-luxury.svg" alt="SUV." />
                    <h1 class="card__h1">LUXURY</h1>
                    <p class="card__p">Cruise in the best car brands without the bloated prices. Enjoy the enhanced comfort of a luxury rental and arrive in style.</p>
                    <button class="card__button card__button--dark-cyan">Learn More</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>